  border-radius: 8px;

  h2 {
    color: #ff3547;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  p {
    color: #333;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  button {
    color: #fff;
    background-color: #ff3547;
    border: none;
    padding: 8px 16px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: background-color 0.3s;

    &:hover {
      background-color: #e02433;
    }
  }
}
```

Ensure that you have the necessary Angular Material modules imported in your application module and that the `ErrorDialogComponent` is declared in the appropriate module. Adjust the styles and structure based on your application's design preferences.